description:
Fixed AI discard logic to properly select multiple cards of same type.

Bug: AI was only discarding 1 card when Militia required discarding down to 3.
Root cause: In engine-strategy.ts line 138, used .find() which only finds ONE card per priority type instead of ALL cards.

Fix: Changed to .filter() to find ALL matching cards, then iterate through them.

Before: const card = options.find(c => c === priority);
After: const matchingCards = options.filter(c => c === priority);
       for (const card of matchingCards) { ... }

Tests: Added comprehensive unit tests in src/strategies/engine-strategy.test.ts
